### Context

During one of my playthroughs of Pokemon XD: Gale of Darkness, I came across an issue with finding the right Pokemon to add to the purify chamber for maximum tempo. So I made a simple csv datasheet of the Pokemon Type Chart in order to make a function to help me solve my issue.
